{"id":660841,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Theory_of_Everything_(2014_movie)","text":"\"The Theory of Everything\" is a 2014 British biographical romantic drama movie directed by James Marsh. It is about the life of the theoretical physicist Stephen Hawking.\nThe movie was based on Jane Hawking's memoir \"Travelling to Infinity: My Life with Stephen\". The movie's score was composed by J\u00F3hann J\u00F3hannsson.\nThe movie stars Eddie Redmayne, Felicity Jones, Charlie Cox, Emily Watson, Simon McBurney, Christian McKay, Harry Lloyd, and David Thewlis. The movie was released on 7 September 2014 at the Toronto International Film Festival and released in the United Kingdom on 1 January 2015 to strong positive reviews.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Biographical","surface_form":"biographical","offset":45},{"uri":"Romantic","surface_form":"romantic","offset":58},{"uri":"Drama","surface_form":"drama","offset":67},{"uri":"James_Marsh_(director)","surface_form":"James Marsh","offset":91},{"uri":"Theoretical_physics","surface_form":"theoretical physicist","offset":132},{"uri":"Stephen_Hawking","surface_form":"Stephen Hawking","offset":154},{"uri":"Jane_Hawking","surface_form":"Jane Hawking","offset":194},{"uri":"Memoir","surface_form":"memoir","offset":209},{"uri":"J%C3%B3hann_J%C3%B3hannsson","surface_form":"J\u00F3hann J\u00F3hannsson","offset":298},{"uri":"Eddie_Redmayne","surface_form":"Eddie Redmayne","offset":333},{"uri":"Felicity_Jones","surface_form":"Felicity Jones","offset":349},{"uri":"Charlie_Cox","surface_form":"Charlie Cox","offset":365},{"uri":"Emily_Watson","surface_form":"Emily Watson","offset":378},{"uri":"Simon_McBurney","surface_form":"Simon McBurney","offset":392},{"uri":"Christian_McKay","surface_form":"Christian McKay","offset":408},{"uri":"Harry_Lloyd","surface_form":"Harry Lloyd","offset":425},{"uri":"David_Thewlis","surface_form":"David Thewlis","offset":442},{"uri":"Toronto_International_Film_Festival","surfac